org.sql: SELECT 1 AS one FROM statuses INNER JOIN media_attachments ON media_attachments.status_id = statuses.id WHERE statuses.account_id = "$1" AND statuses.visibility IN ("$2", "$3") AND statuses.deleted_at IS NULL AND media_attachments.account_id = "$4" GROUP BY statuses.id LIMIT 1 OFFSET "$6"
